# WHAT IT IS
#   couch is a couch-potato-style media-acquisition daemon:
#   it watches a Trakt.tv watchlist for new movies + TV
#   episodes, queries RealDebrid for cached high-quality
#   sources, kicks off the download, and posts progress +
#   completion notifications to a Telegram chat via a Bot
#   API token.  The whole pipeline runs as a single
#   long-lived `couch run` process backed by a local SQLite
#   database; `couch auth` walks the OAuth dance for each
#   external service.
#
#   The Telegram side uses the `go-telegram-bot-api` SDK
#   for sending notifications and accepting inbound
#   `/status` / `/list` / `/cancel` commands.
#
# CLI ARGUMENT GRAMMAR  (verbatim from main.go +
#                       cmd/root.go + cmd/auth.go +
#                       cmd/run.go cobra declarations;
#                       extracted via `gh api repos/nenad/
#                       couch/contents/cmd/...`)
#
#   couch <SUBCOMMAND> [args...]
#
#   Subcommands:
#     run                            Run the application
#                                    (long-lived daemon —
#                                    watches Trakt watchlist
#                                    + processes RealDebrid
#                                    downloads + relays
#                                    Telegram notifications)
#
#     auth <SERVICE>                 Authenticate against an
#                                    external service
#       realdebrid                     Auth procedure for the
#                                      RealDebrid service
#                                      (OAuth device flow)
#       trakt                          Auth procedure for the
#                                      trakt.tv service
#                                      (OAuth device flow)
#       telegram                       Auth procedure for
#                                      Telegram Bot
#                                      notifications (stores
#                                      bot token + chat ID)
#
#   Environment:
#     COUCH_DB                       Path to the SQLite
#                                    database file
#                                    [default: couch.sqlite]
#
#   Standard cobra auto-flags:
#     -h, --help                     Show help (root + each
#                                    subcommand)
#
